            <html:p>
    Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(X, \tau )]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="/gtop-0002/" title="Topological Space" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0002/" display-uri="gtop-0002" type="local">topological space</fr:link>. A subset <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C \subseteq  X]]></fr:tex> is called <html:strong>closed</html:strong> if its complement <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X \setminus  C]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/gtop-0005/" title="Open Set" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0005/" display-uri="gtop-0005" type="local">open</fr:link>, i.e. <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X \setminus  C \in  \tau ]]></fr:tex>.
