              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>
Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(X, d)]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="/gtop-0003/" title="Metric Space" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0003/" display-uri="gtop-0003" type="local">metric space</fr:link> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C \subseteq  X]]></fr:tex>. Then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/gtop-0006/" title="Closed Set" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0006/" display-uri="gtop-0006" type="local">closed</fr:link> if and only if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex> contains all its <fr:link href="/gtop-000T/" title="Limit Point" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000T/" display-uri="gtop-000T" type="local">limit points</fr:link>.
</html:p>
                <html:p>
